generate_ability.prompt_template:
You are designing one new ability for a monster in a fantasy game.

MONSTER:
Name: {monster_name}
Species: {monster_species}
Description: {monster_description}
Personality: {monster_personality}
Party role: {monster_role} | Class: {monster_class} | Elements: {monster_elements}
Deepest wish: {monster_wish}

EXISTING ABILITIES:
{existing_abilities_text}
{growth_context}
Design ONE new ability that fits this monster and differs from its existing abilities. If a reason it is being learned NOW is given above, the ability must grow directly out of that reason.

Pick EVERY field from these options only:
- type: {type_options}
- element: {element_options} | none
- power: {power_options} (weakest to strongest - match the monster, most abilities are modest or potent)
- cost_pool: stamina | mana
- cost: {cost_options} (stronger power should cost more)
- target: {target_options}
- effect (what it mechanically does, pick ONE):
{effect_options}

name: 40 characters or fewer. flavor: EXACTLY ONE vivid sentence, 15 words or fewer - display text only.

Respond with valid JSON in this exact format:
{{"name": "Ability Name", "flavor": "One vivid sentence.", "type": "...", "element": "...", "power": "...", "cost_pool": "...", "cost": "...", "target": "...", "effect": "..."}}

